"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## New Here?\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/oE5KDmMuPNrd4kQBrY48I.png?height=584&width=1517)\\n\\nThe journey of a **Mundo Lingo Manager** begins here. The incubator is a support group where managers network and share knowledge and experience.\\n\\n## Apply\\n\\nNot already in **The Incubator?** First join [Mundo Lingo Collaborators](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/onyNgQAi-2VKGNTDGYK9vf20AK-k7i-3qot58G4Qo54) and then apply to be a **Manager** here:\\n\\n[https://form.typeform.com/to/G1bjAQ?typeform-source=mundolingo.org](https://form.typeform.com/to/G1bjAQ?typeform-source=mundolingo.org)\\n\\n**Already in Residency? Continue below‚Ä¶**\\n\\n\\n---\\n\\n## üì£ Communication\\n\\nCommunication is **key** to your success here. \\n\\nCheck out our community [guide on Communication](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/QqxhcUkKracAP2iHqr0dOFiVCDuQiSiAVcEGSv_xD7E) before you begin.\\n\\n## üëã Introduce yourself\\n\\nIntroduce yourself to the Incubator group. This is a **must**. Be noticed - Light up the sky üåü, don‚Äôt let anyone not-notice you arrived ‚ú®\\n\\n* Who are you?\\n* What are your passions, hobbies, interests?\\n* How did you get here?\\n* Why are you here?\\n* What are you interested in?\\n* Who are you interested in connecting with?\\n* What skills -if any- can you offer to other members?\\n\\n## Participate and Learn\\n\\n### Use the EOM\\n\\nThe [Events Operations Manual (EOM)](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/QhvLl3HKyYJ2Z1TVX-rwDjVhwLhwX-QNyRHawRUYZFE) aims to collect all the information you could possibly need to be an amazing Manager. Please read it carefully, raise questions about it in the Incubator group if you have any.\\n\\n### Scrums\\n\\n‚è∞ **Weekly**, alternating between **Friday 12AM and Tuesday 12PM GMT** Let‚Äôs get to know each other! [Scrums](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/63i6GPIBoYjId039yeEXMwNFTWVVL0Mjjj6WPrrJhDE) are our time to speak face to face, listen to each other, learn about each others progress and try to answer questions others may have. [More here‚Ä¶](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/63i6GPIBoYjId039yeEXMwNFTWVVL0Mjjj6WPrrJhDE)\\n\\n### Ask for help\\n\\nDon‚Äôt ask - don‚Äôt get. We‚Äôre here to help. Ask questions, don‚Äôt suffer in shyness!\\n\\n### Use Google\\n\\nDon‚Äôt be that guy/gal who asks *‚Äúwhat does the flag for Iran look like?‚Äù.* If you do, you‚Äôll probably get what you deserve :)\\n\\n### Help Others, Be Supportive.\\n\\nGreat ways to raise your presence in the group\\n\\n1. Give new members a **warm welcome**. Give them with your personal intro.\\n2. Have a go at answering peoples questions\\n3. Even if you don‚Äôt know, let them know *‚Äòhey that‚Äôs a great question‚Äô!*\\n\\n![Successful Managers support one another](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/DMfN9YsDh1DoNf19Iy_AX.png?height=677&width=1470)\\n\\n### Presence Level\\n\\nNobody is checking on you, only you. Be conscious of your own presence level, if it‚Äôs high you will find many friends to help you in your time of need. If to the contrary, it can begin to feel intimidating to speak.\\n\\n![Harold wasn't very present](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/xZ-F3febC12gi6Dr0KMNH.png?height=395&width=1172)\\n\\n## Roadmap Overview\\n\\nSo you‚Äôre wondering when to start and what to to. Here‚Äôs a birds eye view of the road ahead for incoming Managers.\\n\\n1. Venue Investigation\\n2. Receive Flags\\n3. Confirm Venue\\n4. Confirm Team\\n5. Pass Speech Test\\n6. Marketing Setup\\n7. Launch\\n\\n## Help the next generation\\n\\nNew Managers come in all the time and face the same struggles that are now behind you. How could your experience have been easier, and how can we apply that to newbies?\\n\\nWays you can help:\\n\\n* Make suggestions to amend current guides ***\\\\[link needed\\\\]***\\n* Write a guide covering a subject not yet covered ***\\\\[link needed\\\\]***\\n* Volunteer to lead a working group ***\\\\[link needed\\\\]***\\n* Keep giving hearty warm welcomes to newbies!  ‚ù§Ô∏è\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/2-XV4fhLg6NN1e0CXAJEl.png?height=300&width=1150)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1639559762,\"title\":\"The Incubator\"},\"digest\":\"Q4_d3L1iu4UJft_TmMA1RvkF0eUn05DsJ0uQdUUfg48\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"34suyCfnLUoFM02SOhmJJJ9iXgiiL5kC6iPH6Fv3LXk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"jtVAiplEVAd0RPMj7L2P0umm9wTPdvk-kh1vAJTvwJc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"s6B4dEd80hLvjiKM9EPLqDwCMTbFzDMvTv7TWbLjKQaa7lQpKSYAy3VHzxZDiFAWFiV4OntvcVSnonlfcNIrmQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x57d0f7cbea22222afabed23e09ac819f759269ea4cca2a83cdd992ddf3ffe88d22a7afd325b70c3c1ae7dee6f5fc8e22188ba69c589cf1f0528e258261121ae51b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"34suyCfnLUoFM02SOhmJJJ9iXgiiL5kC6iPH6Fv3LXk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"jtVAiplEVAd0RPMj7L2P0umm9wTPdvk-kh1vAJTvwJc\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"u9k391Q69s4h51bqyDa5GDeG7HurDVXaOuhFcHcb-Jc\"}"